	x$type[x$pic_type== &quot;item&quot; &amp;&amp; x$roi==&quot;relation&quot; ]  =&quot;empty&quot;
	x$type[x$pic_type== &quot;relation&quot; &amp;&amp; x$roi==&quot;object&quot; ]  =&quot;empty&quot;
	return(x)
} 
```

Also for setting your type you used `==` which performs comparisons, but for assignments you have to use single `=`.

